{"tid":1458470,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【逆權運動】男子遭打甩門牙 克警不理哀求膝跪頭部壓地至滿口鮮血","createTime":"2019-08-12T14:06:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T13:25:41.000Z","uid":156878,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"178a2e4f1d4e120edb9d0cb3d4d4d1b1e40cfe93","tid":1458470,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:06:41.000Z","msg":"疑似有警察在銅鑼灣喬裝混入示威者之中，並制服多人，其中有人被拘捕時口部已不斷流血，該男子多次表示已知悉被捕，多次哀求該疑似警察不要再施暴，但仍遭粗暴對待。<br />\n<br />\n根據港大學生會學苑拍攝到的片段，一名男子在軒尼詩道希慎廣場對開的地方，被兩名警員制服。男子口中不停流血，並向警察哭訴指「對唔住，我知道喇」、「我已經畀你拉咗」、「我門牙都甩埋喇，唔好撳喇我求吓你」，其間有人問男子：「你係咪畀警察打」對方一度回應「係」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922006\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922006&d=1ZU4T503J%2FBBtE%2F0CauWlS2wsmw0HNSHoQ%2FRl4ZEJbA%3D&h=59f0d84e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190812%2F59922006&h=d5eacd6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190812/59922006</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然被射爆眼既女仔令人好憤怒, 但大家好似都冇遺忘左佢. 被人整爆門牙, 成地血都仲要被差佬虐待.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f76674aaa70cc625409ab4688b04ce5c93fad2","tid":1458470,"uid":156878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T14:07:30.000Z","msg":"雖然被射爆眼既女仔令人好憤怒, 但大家好似都遺忘左佢. 被人整爆門牙, 成地血都仲要被差佬虐待.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a225c33a6a069438895926603bcee53e66f6e70